Djangolib
=========


Installation
------------

.. code-block:: bash

    pip install unicef-djangolib


Setup
-----

Add ``unicef_djangolib`` to ``INSTALLED_APPS`` in settings

.. code-block:: bash

    INSTALLED_APPS = [
        ...
        'unicef_djangolib',
    ]


